channel.title: Praise and Worship Music Live at Without Walls International Church (Video)
channel.description: Without Walls International Church is located in Tampa, Florida. Pastor Paula White is the senior pastor of WWIC. Dr. Mark Payne is the Fine Art Director of WWIC. This podcast is recorded within the WWIC sanctuary during services on Thursdays and Sundays.

item.title: March 27th, Sunday morning at Without Walls International Church in Tampa
item.description: Without Walls International Church Fine Arts directed by Dr. Mark Payne lead the congregation in five songs. Give Hime Praises by William McDowell. How Great is Our God by Chris Tomlin. Nobody Greater by Vashawn Mitchell. Your Name is Above All Names by Vashawn Mitchell. Alpha and Omega by Israel and New Breed.
